    "en": {
      "title": "Beheading of a lonely elderly woman; Incident in Kankesanthurai",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kankesanthurai - An elderly woman who was alone at home in Kollangalatti was found dead today (Friday) with cuts on her neck.",
        "Kankesanthurai police said the motive for the murder could not be ascertained as the jewelery worn by the elderly woman was found in a non-looted condition.",
        "A relative who went to fetch water from the garden in the grandmother's house premises on Friday morning informed the Kankesanthurai police that an elderly woman was found dead with bloody wounds."
